{"tid":2182441,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"2021 Master of Nursing","createTime":"2020-08-31T09:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T11:56:51.000Z","uid":107800,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"31f709ae118b7c35ef20b1bcc9f068e569934c7b","tid":2182441,"uid":107800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:55:35.000Z","msg":"中大 9月1日開放報名啦！<br />\n準備好文件同2封推薦信未呀？<br />\n<br />\n中大：<a href=\"http://www.nur.cuhk.edu.hk/education/postgraduate-programmes/master-of-nursing-science-pre-registration/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nur.cuhk.edu.hk%2Feducation%2Fpostgraduate-programmes%2Fmaster-of-nursing-science-pre-registration%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr04dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=9278601d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nur.cuhk.edu.hk/education/postgraduate-programmes/master-of-nursing-science-pre-registration/</a><br />\nTuition Fee<br />\nHK$130,000 per annum<br />\nHK$390,000 for 3 years <br />\n<br />\nMode of Study<br />\nFull-time: 3 years<br />\n<br />\nAdmission Requirements<br />\nHave a bachelor&rsquo;s degree in any discipline from a recognised university, normally with honours not lower than Second Class (or equivalent); and<br />\nHave a good command of written and spoken English and Chinese (Cantonese); and<br />\nFulfil English Language and other requirements stipulated by the Graduate School of CUHK (please visit <a href=\"https://www.gs.cuhk.edu.hk/admissions/admissions/requirements\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gs.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fadmissions%2Fadmissions%2Frequirements&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr04dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=e8619231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gs.cuhk.edu.hk/admissions/admissions/requirements</a> for details); and<br />\nFulfil the entry requirement stipulated by the NCHK; and<br />\nAttend an interview (if necessary).<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理大<a href=\"https://sn.polyu.edu.hk/en/programmes/postgraduate_studies/master_of_nursing/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsn.polyu.edu.hk%2Fen%2Fprogrammes%2Fpostgraduate_studies%2Fmaster_of_nursing%2Findex.html&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr04dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=4773f782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sn.polyu.edu.hk/en/programmes/postgraduate_studies/master_of_nursing/index.html</a><br />\nTuition Fee<br />\n96 credits x $3800 per credit = HK$364,800 for 3 years <br />\n<br />\nMode of Study<br />\nFull-time: 3 years<br />\n<br />\nEntrance Requirements<br />\nHong Kong Certificate of Education Examination, or the equivalent.<br />\nEnglish Language (Syllabus B) at Grade D or above, or English Language (Syllabus A) at Grade B, or English Language at Level 3;<br />\nAny one science subject from the following at Grade E or above: Biology, Chemistry, Human Biology, Mathematics, Physics;<br />\nAny three other subjects at Grade E (or Level 2 for Chinese Language) or above; and<br />\nAny one of the subjects listed in (1) to (3) must be at Grade C (or Level 3 for English Language or Chinese Language) or above.<br />\n/<br />\nFor Hong Kong Diploma of Secondary Education Examination, applicants are required to have satisfied the following or the equivalent.<br />\n4 core subjects, with English Language and Chinese Language at Level 3 or above, and Mathematics and Liberal Studies at Level 2 or above; and<br />\n1 elective subject from Category A - New Senior Secondary Subjects at Level 2 or above.<br />\nFluency in written English and Chinese, and in oral English and Cantonese.<br />\n<br />\nPreferred Subjects<br />\nThere are no preferred subjects in the selection process. All subjects will be considered."},{"pid":"55de8d6ee21caab32cf2f1bd203df2dd405c6489","tid":2182441,"uid":155684,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:58:44.000Z","msg":"終於開啦，希望入到Poly<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d6ad60dbafbe5516